data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to your dream home by Luckey Lake, US90, plus it is a short trip to Lackland AFB and Sea World! This stunning two-story, 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence is a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Step inside and be captivated by this beautiful home. The galley kitchen, adorned with stainless steel appliances, is a culinary enthusiast's haven. From preparing a quick breakfast to hosting a gourmet dinner, this kitchen is your canvas! All three bedrooms are conveniently situated upstairs, providing privacy and tranquility. Each room is equipped with its own ceiling fan, ensuring a comfortable atmosphere year-round. No more hauling laundry up and down the stairs - the upstairs laundry room adds a touch of practicality to your daily routine. Step out into the spacious backyard, where endless possibilities await. With ample space and a covered patio, you can effortlessly host outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or simply unwind and soak in the serene ambiance. The icing on the cake? The fantastic location. Nestled close to Luckey Lake and US90, you'll have easy access to natural beauty and convenient travel routes. Whether you're a nature lover, a commuter, or both, this location caters to all your needs. Don't miss this opportunity to make this wonderful house your home.
